This paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and data mining (cs.DM) sub-categories as it proposes heuristics for optimizing the $k$-means objective function. It also involves clustering, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and computer vision (cs.CV).
